        <updateDate>2022-02-18T20:38:27Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>September 11 Transparency Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill requires declassification reviews of certain documents related to investigations into the terrorist attacks on September 11, 2001.</p> <p>The Office of the Director of National Intelligence, the Department of Justice, and the Central Intelligence Agency must complete reviews of certain documents by deadlines specified in the bill.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
